Name: Super Agent: Drunk Kent
About the game: Super Agent: Drunk Kent is a take on the classic platformer elements of old, with a physics based twist. Our hero (the greatest Agent on the side of good) does his best work.....plastered! Enamored by the intoxication of alcohol! Sloshed! However, in this state he can; Jump, dodge, hone his reflexes and slow time, and survive all the devious traps one could find being a Secret Agent! Physics based Platforming.. Drunken Slo-mo.. Over twenty custom made music tracks.. Classic platforming elements.. Physics puzzles.. Cunning retro A.I.. Totally physics based movement.. Distinct worlds to explore and survive.. Full Controller Support.. Hand Drawn Pixel Art.. Environment Based Traps..
